eu.eexcess.insa.peas

Class CacheReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.eexcess.insa.peas.CacheReader

  • public class CacheReader
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to read caches. It allows reading the co-occurrence graph cache and the maximal cliques graph. The locations of cache files are given in the configuration file.
    Version:
    2.0
    Author:
    Thomas Cerqueus
